Class FilledShape

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
EllipseShape, PolygonShape, RectangleShape
public abstract class FilledShape
extends EdgedShape
implements java.lang.Cloneable

The FilledShape class represents shapes that have a fill and edge color in 2D space. The colors are specified through Color objects.
